    "pseudocode":  "FLOW Microflow: ExcelImporter.Sub_CreateColumnsFromTemplate\r\nNODES=10; EDGES=8\r\n1. START\r\n2. ACTION RetrieveAction: retrieve MxObjectType over association Template_MxObjectType from Template\r\n3. ACTION CreateVariableAction: create variable AutoNumberToBeIgnored=MxModelReflection.PrimitiveTypes.AutoNumber\r\n4. ACTION RetrieveAction: retrieve MemberList from MxModelReflection.MxObjectMember\r\n5. ACTION RetrieveAction: retrieve ColumnList over association Column_Template from Template\r\n6. ACTION AggregateListAction: AggregateListAction (output=NextColNumber, errorHandlingType=Rollback)\r\n7. LOOP iterate MemberList as Member\r\n  8. LOOP BODY\r\n    9. ACTION ListOperationAction: ListOperationAction (output=Column, errorHandlingType=Rollback)\r\n    10. ACTION ChangeObjectAction: change Column (MappingType=ExcelImporter.MappingType.Attribute, FindAttribute=$Member/AttributeName, Column_MxObjectMember=$Member, Column_MxObjectType=$MxObjectType; refreshInClient=false)\r\n    11. ACTION CreateObjectAction: create ExcelImporter.Column as NewColumn (ColNumber=$NextColNumber, Text=$ColumnTitle, Column_Template=$Template)\r\n    12. ACTION ChangeListAction: change ColumnList (type=Add, value=$NewColumn)\r\n    13. ACTION CreateVariableAction: create variable ColumnTitle=$Member/AttributeName\r\n    14. DECISION found? expression=$Column != empty\r\n    15. NODE ExclusiveMerge: ExclusiveMerge\r\n    16. ACTION ChangeVariableAction: change variable NextColNumber=if $NextColNumber = empty then 0 else $NextColNumber + 1\r\n17. ACTION CommitAction: commit ColumnList (refreshInClient=true, withEvents=true)\r\n18. END",
